---
/**
 * The Offer — Mafia Offer breakdown (Hormozi-style)
 * Every deliverable named, categorised, and justified.
 */
---

<section id="offer" class="py-32 relative bg-white">
  <div class="section-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600 mb-4">
        What You Actually Get
      </p>
      <h2
        class="font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-e2-black tracking-tight mb-6"
      >
        The Full Revenue Engine.<br />
        <span class="text-gray-400">Built Once. Yours Forever.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500">
        Most agencies give you a retainer and a vague promise.<br />
        We hand you a complete, battle-tested email & SMS machine — and walk away.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Deliverable Cards -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Card 1: Revenue Flows -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg"
          >
            ⚡
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600"
            >
              Block 1
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-e2-black">
              4 Core Revenue Flows
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-5">
          The four flows that account for 80% of automated revenue in every DTC
          brand. Built, tested, live.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {
            [
              [
                "Welcome Series",
                "Converts cold subscribers into first-time buyers within 7 days.",
              ],
              [
                "Abandoned Checkout",
                "Recovers buyers who were seconds away from purchasing.",
              ],
              [
                "Added to Cart",
                "Catches high-intent browsers before they leave.",
              ],
              [
                "Browse Abandonment",
                "Re-engages window shoppers with the right message at the right time.",
              ],
            ].map(([name, desc]) => (
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs flex-shrink-0">
                  ✓
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-e2-black text-sm">
                    {name}
                  </span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">{desc}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Nurture + Consumable -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg"
          >
            🔁
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-600"
            >
              Block 2
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-e2-black">
              Nurture + Consumable Flow
            </h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-5">
          Turn one-time buyers into repeat customers — automatically.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {
            [
              [
                "Nurture Sequence",
                "Builds trust, educates, and primes your list to buy again. Runs on autopilot after every purchase.",
              ],
              [
                "Consumable Replenishment Flow",
                "Timed to your product's use cycle. If they ordered an energy drink 3 weeks ago, we remind them before they run out — not after. Drives reorders without a single manual send.",
              ],
            ].map(([name, desc]) => (
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs flex-shrink-0">
                  ✓
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-e2-black text-sm">
                    {name}
                  </span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">{desc}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: The Team -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-violet-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg"
          >
            🎯
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-600"
            >
              Block 3
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-e2-black">The Team Behind It</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-5">
          You don't get a junior VA. You get a full senior team.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {
            [
              [
                "Dedicated Performance Strategist",
                "Owns your account. Accountable to your numbers.",
              ],
              [
                "World-Class Copywriter (Zero AI)",
                "Human-written copy that sounds like your brand, not a chatbot.",
              ],
              [
                "Senior Graphic Designer",
                "On-brand email design that converts.",
              ],
              [
                "Klaviyo Technical Specialist",
                "Handles all setup, segmentation, and deliverability.",
              ],
            ].map(([name, desc]) => (
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-violet-100 text-violet-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs flex-shrink-0">
                  ✓
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-e2-black text-sm">
                    {name}
                  </span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">{desc}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: The Guarantee Stack -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg"
          >
            🛡️
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-600"
            >
              Block 4
            </p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-e2-black">The Risk Reversal</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-5">
          We only win when you win. Here's how we back that up.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          {
            [
              [
                "Full IP Ownership",
                "Every flow, every email, every asset — yours. Forever.",
              ],
              [
                "No Monthly Retainer",
                "One flat fee. No ongoing invoices. No lock-in.",
              ],
              [
                "Deliverability & DNS Audit",
                "We fix your sending reputation before we send a single email.",
              ],
              [
                "Profit-First A/B Testing",
                "We test to increase revenue, not open rates.",
              ],
            ].map(([name, desc]) => (
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <div class="mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs flex-shrink-0">
                  ✓
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold text-e2-black text-sm">
                    {name}
                  </span>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5">{desc}</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            ))
          }
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Total Value Summary + CTA -->
    <div
      class="max-w-2xl mx-auto rounded-3xl bg-e2-black text-white p-10 text-center shadow-2xl shadow-black/20"
    >
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400 mb-3">
        The Mafia Offer
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3 tracking-tight">
        6 Flows. A Full Senior Team.<br />One Flat Fee. Yours to Keep.
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        4 revenue flows + 1 nurture sequence + 1 consumable replenishment flow.<br
        />
        Built by a dedicated strategist, copywriter, designer & Klaviyo specialist.<br
        />
        No retainer. No lock-in. 100% IP ownership.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-8">
        Most agencies charge $3,000–$8,000/month for a fraction of this. We do
        it once. Book a call to get your number.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0/appointments/schedules/AcZssZ2R0f..."
        class="inline-block px-10 py-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-e2-black font-bold text-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform shadow-xl"
      >
        See If You Qualify — Book a Free Call →
      </a>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4">
        Fully refundable if we don't identify at least 20% growth potential in
        your first call.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
